gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Kings 125, Lakers 110
gameRecap.excerpt: The Kings defeated the Lakers, 125-110. Domantas Sabonis recorded 29 points, 16 rebounds, and 7 assists for the Kings, with DeAaron Fox (28 points, 5 assists) and Kevin Huerter (28 points, 7 assists) combined for 56 points in the victory. LeBron James tallied 28 points, 11 assists, and 10 rebounds for the Lakers in the losing effort. The Kings improve to 6-4 on the season, while the Lakers fall to 6-6.
